cdata.name: FunFair
cdata.desc: FunFair is an Ethereum-based casino that allows users to bet in a trustless and decentralized model, featuing3D games can be built in HTML5. FunFair offers cheap fees in terms of gas costs.TheFUN coin is also an Ethereum-based token that will be used for all platform actions, including betting, lending, paying out players and compensating stakeholders.
